org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.mxml

Class MXMLManifestManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.mxml.MXMLManifestManager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IMXMLManifestManager

    public class MXMLManifestManager
extends Object
implements IMXMLManifestManager
    Each FlexProject has an MXMLManifestManager to resolve MXML tags to ActionScript classes, using the tags inside SWCs' catalog.xml files and any manifest files associated with the project. This manager must be recreated whenever the library path, or a manifest file, changes.
